data.description:
Don't miss this rare opportunity to own TWO homes with a 15 SPACE MOBILE HOME PARK!! Let's talk about the park first! The potential is endless. This park has his and her bathrooms with showers. Large laundry room. Commercial size propane tank for guests at the park or other residents near by can fill up their small tanks. To the back of this property runs a beautiful creek for all to enjoy. Certain areas have a beach like entrance. 

First home has an open concept with granite counter tops and beautiful white cabinets. Large fireplace for those cozy nights. Large master bedroom with large walk-in closet. 

Second home has large living room also with an open concept to the kitchen. Hard wood floors. Stainless steel countertops. Large bedrooms and bath. 

The grounds on this property are like no other in this area. Very well maintained. Wonderful outdoor entertainment area. Several outdoor shops for storage. This property would be wonderful to Airbnb, you could also add tiny homes in the mobile home spaces to create more income and still have a home for your own vacation use if wanted!!

California Hot Springs is known for its natural hot springs. California Hot Springs Resort was recently bought out by the well known ''Artistree'' artistreehome.com the community is ready for this transformation. Also, you have Trail of 100 Giants Gateway to the Giant Sequoia's only about 15 miles up the road!! 

Lots more to explore so schedule your private showing with your favorite Realtor today!!
